asset.author: iRobot
asset.hookText: We've been trying to get Meezle (aka "Meezle Maid") on film forever when she vacuums using the Roomba, but she usually bolts when you pick up the camera. This time, she "allowed" me to film her. She can also shut it off when she wants. She was sniffing it to see if it was cleaned out. ... She doesn't care to use it if it's full. She knows the right buttons to push and since it's excellent for removing pet hair from the rug (and we have seven cats), she pulls her own weight.  Now if she could only learn to empty it.....
